desc: Ananda Food is an Australian owned company with over 20 years of experience. We work alongside Australian farmers to produce the safest, best quality hemp products on the market. When we’re not on the farm, we’re spending time with family.

layout.text:
Australian Major Scale Producer
of Food-Grade Hemp Products
We are committed to delivering the highest quality and affordable Australian grown hemp foods to support sustainable plant-based innovation while improving your health and wellbeing.
